            <title>[LU-9213] /etc/init.d/lustre status is partial for MGT</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9213</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With MGT and MDT split across MDS&apos;s, the MDS with the MGT reports &quot;partial&quot; when running /etc/init.d/lustre . There are tests for MDT, OST, and clients, in which case they (should) report &quot;running&quot;. It was expected that all servers would report &quot;running&quot; when in a normal state.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
